<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Smart Health — Klinik Digital Terpercaya</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="landing-nav">
    <div class="landing-nav-brand">
      <span class="landing-nav-brand-icon">&#10010;</span> Smart<strong>Health</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="landing-nav-actions">
      <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Masuk</a>
      <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Daftar Gratis</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="landing-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="landing-hero-eyebrow">&#127973; Sistem Klinik Terpadu</span>
      <h1 class="landing-hero-title">Reservasi dokter dan rekam medis dalam <span class="accent">satu sistem</span>.</h1>
      <p class="landing-hero-desc">
        Smart Health menghubungkan pasien, dokter, dan admin klinik dalam satu alur kerja —
        mulai dari booking jadwal, pencatatan diagnosis, resep digital, sampai laporan medis
        yang bisa diunduh kapan saja.
      </p>
      <div class="landing-hero-actions">
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-primary">Buat Akun Pasien</a>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline">Saya Sudah Punya Akun</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="landing-hero-visual">
      <span class="landing-visual-pill">&#9889; Live</span>
      <div class="landing-visual-card">
        <div class="landing-visual-card-title">Appointment Hari Ini</div>
        <div class="landing-visual-card-value">12 Pasien</div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-visual-card">
        <div class="landing-visual-card-title">Dokter Aktif</div>
        <div class="landing-visual-card-value">8 Spesialis</div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-visual-card">
        <div class="landing-visual-card-title">Rekam Medis Tercatat</div>
        <div class="landing-visual-card-value">340+</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="landing-features">
    <h2 class="landing-section-title">Satu sistem, tiga peran</h2>
    <p class="landing-section-desc">Dirancang agar pasien, dokter, dan admin punya alur kerja masing-masing yang relevan.</p>

    <div class="grid-row grid-3">
      <div class="landing-feature-card">
        <div class="landing-feature-icon">&#128100;</div>
        <div class="landing-feature-title">Untuk Pasien</div>
        <div class="landing-feature-desc">Cari dokter sesuai spesialisasi, booking jadwal tanpa bentrok, lihat riwayat rekam medis dan resep, lalu unduh sebagai PDF.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-feature-card">
        <div class="landing-feature-icon">&#9879;</div>
        <div class="landing-feature-title">Untuk Dokter</div>
        <div class="landing-feature-desc">Kelola jadwal praktik, lihat antrian appointment, isi diagnosis dan resep langsung dari sistem.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="landing-feature-card">
        <div class="landing-feature-icon">&#9635;</div>
        <div class="landing-feature-title">Untuk Admin</div>
        <div class="landing-feature-desc">Kelola data dokter, pantau seluruh appointment, dan lihat statistik klinik lewat dashboard visual.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
